high_descs: Walk straight towards the couch, turn right towards the middle of it, and turn right to face a coffee table.
Pick up the tissue box on the table.
Turn right towards the couch, turn left towards the tall lamp on your right.
anns.task_desc: Examine a tissue box next to the light of a tall lamp.

high_descs: Walk to the front of the coffee table to the right.
Pick up the tissue box from the coffee table.
Walk around the coffee table and stand in front of the floor lamp by the sofa.
anns.task_desc: Examine a tissue box by the light of a floor lamp.

high_descs: Walk forward and turn right to stand facing the coffee table with your back to the couch.
Pick up  the tissue box from the coffee table.
Walk to the right, then left, to the lamp in the corner of the room.
anns.task_desc: Look at a box of tissues by the lamp.
